creator: DLP GROUP
descriptionHtml:
With the mobile app your Tor-ba stores are now even closer. You become our loyal and valued customer by using the new Tor-ba app.

The app enables you to:
- Receive discounts, cash-back, bonuses and gifts tailored just for you
- Amass and spend bonuses by making purchases across our chain of supermarkets
- Visit our online store in-app
- Be up to date with the company news and events
- Receive feedback on your inquiries and suggestions
- Move up the ranks to get improved terms of participation in the loyalty program
- Pay with your bonuses instead of money
descriptionShort: Isn’t it convenient to have your favorite supermarket close by?
